description: Cypress Development Corp. engages in the acquisition, exploration, evaluation, and development of mineral properties in the United States and Canada. It explores for lithium, zinc, and silver deposits. The company's flagship project is the Clayton Valley project that covers an area of approximately 5,430 acres located in southwest Nevada. Cypress Development Corp. was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Dr. William Wesley Willoughby PE, Ph.D.
